This paper discusses the implementation of access control mechanisms in medical imaging repositories, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and data management (cs.DB). The use of Cloud services also suggests a possible connection to cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper also mentions the use of web services for management, which falls under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper proposes an ownership concept, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE).
